    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Rot-beasts are shambling horrors of living corruption — flesh and root and fungus fused together by the Rot's influence on the Green Heart. They lumber forward with terrible purpose, dealing corruption damage with every strike and surrounded by a decay aura that causes living tissue to founder. They are not undead but something worse: still-living creatures warped beyond recognition, animated by the Rot's hunger for growth.</p>",
